# EmlakMaster onboarding assets
# Add PNG or WebP images (1600x1600 or 2048x2048) for Retina/high-DPI.
# If a file is missing, the app shows a premium placeholder with icon + floating cards.
#
# Expected filenames:
#   crm_dashboard.png   - Dashboard / command center
#   market_analytics.png - Market Pulse & listings
#   ai_insights.png     - AI & analytics
#   war_room.png        - War Room & call center
#
# Optimize for production: convert PNG to WebP (cwebp) or use Flutter's asset
# compression to reduce first-load time. Current PNGs ~1–1.5 MB each.
